ERROR HANDLING RULES:
- Any single source fails → log warning, skip source, continue others
- Any single internship check fails → log reason, move to REJECTED, continue
- Network timeout on verification → infra_failure, do NOT reject company for it
- openpyxl write error → retry once, then log and exit cleanly
- Script must NEVER crash entirely from one bad internship

---

ABSOLUTE RULES:
1. NEVER write fake stipend values
2. NEVER write plain "LINK" text without real hyperlink
3. NEVER write expired internships to active tabs
4. NEVER write unpaid internships to active tabs
5. NEVER write fraud internships to active tabs
6. NEVER crash on single bad internship — catch all exceptions per item
7. ALWAYS recalculate Sr. No. cleanly per tab before saving
8. ALWAYS save output file even if 0 internships found (empty tabs ok)
9. DO NOT import any library not listed above
10. DO NOT add database dependency — this is standalone script only

---

